'''單寧體'''（{{lang-en|tannosome}}，或称'''鞣质体'''）是一种在[[维管植物|维管植物]]细胞内存在的[[细胞器|细胞器]]。

==生理作用==
單寧體是一种制造并存储{{tsl|en|Condensed tannin|缩合鞣质|缩合}}[[鞣质|鞣质]]和[[多酚|多酚]]的[[色素体|色素体]]。这些色素体可以和[[叶绿体|叶绿体]]互相转换。存储的鞣质和多酚可以作为化学物质帮植物驱赶[[食草动物|食草动物]]，如[[蚜虫|蚜虫]]。鞣质还可以保护植物免受[[病原体|病原体]]和[[紫外线|紫外线]]的危害。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.the-scientist.com/?articles.view/articleNo/37597/title/New-Organelle--The-Tannosome/ |title = New Organelle: The Tannosome |author = Kerry Grens |date = 2013-09-23 |publisher = The Scientist Magazine® |accessdate = 2014-08-22 |archive-date = 2014-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140307150925/http://www.the-scientist.com/?articles.view%2FarticleNo%2F37597%2Ftitle%2FNew-Organelle--The-Tannosome%2F |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 发现 ==
在2013年，一群法国的研究人员在植物试管的鞣质聚集处发现了單寧體。<ref>http://aob.oxfordjournals.org/content/early/2013/09/11/aob.mct168.full.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://aob.oxfordjournals.org/content/early/2013/09/11/aob.mct168.full.pdf |date=20131228233227 }} Annals of Botany: The tannosome is an organelle forming condensed tannins in the chlorophyllous organs of Tracheophyta</ref>

